Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.82,0:00:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.01,0:00:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「利落」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.40,0:00:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Necro・Macro」總算又重新啟動了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可等了很長時間呦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.94,0:00:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前沒少受你照顧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.37,0:01:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欠你的如數奉還 也算了結了我一樁心願
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.16,0:01:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人就是 紅衣男
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.34,0:01:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅衣…男
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.10,0:01:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.27,0:01:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非 這傢伙就是「啄木鳥」?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.36,0:01:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你是不想等到明天了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.58,0:01:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.84,0:01:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血之刃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.84,0:02:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「罪之枝」 「Crow・烏鴉」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.28,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.28,0:03:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前幾天的死肉祭還蠻有看頭的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.28,0:03:47.03,eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(599,644)}Carnival Corpse
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次的賭注不小心下多了 緊張了一把呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是呢 明天 期待已久的新人終於要登場了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:04:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新人「啄木鳥」將會與「烏鴉」進行對戰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可值得期待啊 我老婆可是「烏鴉」的粉絲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.39,0:04:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 請貴夫婦務必一同欣賞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.26,0:04:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個「啄木鳥」 是個怎樣的「Deadman」呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.02,0:04:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊 您還是親自欣賞比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.48,0:04:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真會故弄玄虛啊 又是老一套嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是搞不過你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我先告辭一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉打擾您會客
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有情況發生了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G棟的舊避難所前「烏鴉」正在發飆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像 在切披薩一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.06,0:04:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙 就是那時的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:05:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就如你所願
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我們稍微為明天來個熱身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「啄木鳥」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.82,0:05:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你願意 認真地打一場也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.66,0:05:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說與在中庭時的打扮不太一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你一言不發傻站在那幹啥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.72,0:05:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.16,0:05:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會被殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.71,0:05:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 別讓我Orz好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是那個「啄木鳥」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.21,0:06:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啄木……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把全班同學都殺掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.18,0:06:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長野的（嗶嗶=瘋子）初中生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算把「罪之枝」留到何時
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都出了這麼多血了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血? 這樣說的話 剛才
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 是血
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那股力量是需要血的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:50.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 我白期待了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.26,0:06:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我失望也要有個限度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.85,0:06:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無趣的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.78,0:07:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.25,0:07:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要為我的朋友 山炸排和美美報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.17,0:07:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅衣男
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.37,0:07:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那究竟是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 為什麼會無效啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.76,0:08:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你「利落」地正中了我的心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼仇啊 紅衣男啊 我都不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.14,0:08:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你挺能打啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.39,0:08:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦? 什麼叫「不知道」…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.27,0:08:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 他不是紅衣男
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊? 我哪裡紅啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那個力量 在學校把我的朋友們都…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了你朋友的是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.83,0:08:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在亂七八糟說些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我 我沒有殺人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.76,0:08:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我才以為你是當時的犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:09:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是「烏鴉」 千地清正
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不知道你把我和誰搞混了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.68,0:09:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「罪之枝」的話 你不也能用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 莫非
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.07,0:09:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為只有你和那個紅衣男是「Deadman」?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Deadman」…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.87,0:09:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在「死囚樂園」的最中央
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個G棟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.16,0:09:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為關的都是些什麽傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.34,0:09:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么會…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.38,0:09:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你什麼也不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會以為只有自己才是特殊的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有壞掉的大人和小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.27,0:09:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對 你就是小鬼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 來陪我「利落」地玩玩吧 「啄木鳥」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.46,0:10:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許欺負丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.59,0:10:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女 女人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.30,0:10:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 許 欺 負 丸 太
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.64,0:10:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我知道啦 穿上這個 你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.73,0:10:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.89,0:10:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全身緊身衣不太好吧 各種不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.36,0:10:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你欺負丸太的話白就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.78,0:10:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 晃起來了 我說晃起來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他真的不是紅衣男嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.14,0:11:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸 丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.68,0:11:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們 別來妨礙我打…架
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.19,0:11:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太 丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.32,0:11:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白醬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G棟門前清理完畢 全員捕獲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 那個9061號 讓他走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.64,0:11:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎你那邊不太好處理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.93,0:11:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那個…別亂動…行了…跟我走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 創辦人 有一個人沒有識別代碼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.57,0:12:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 管理服務器出錯了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒔名長官 又要生氣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒有?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.96,0:12:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 不僅是「Necro・Macro」的殘骸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連犯人的腳印和指紋 都沒有找到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.63,0:12:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那隻老狐狸幹的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到底想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒔名長官 您要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.06,0:12:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去見所長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.35,0:12:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 按照規定 您必須要取得創始人的許可
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論受到處分還是被解雇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.74,0:12:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不找他直接面談的話 我是不會罷休的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.65,0:12:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是因為規定 而是為了紀律
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 丸太在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:12:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了正帶你過去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.67,0:13:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不准再亂來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,監視那幫人就夠受的了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.88,0:13:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 為什麼要隱藏G棟的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.06,0:13:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊? 那是當然的了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那群傢伙很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.52,0:13:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡的所有人 可都是「罪之枝」的發病者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罪的…發病…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.07,0:13:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是疾病什麼的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.86,0:13:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天知道 具體情況我們也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.78,0:13:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Deadman」 血之能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.54,0:13:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個監獄到底是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.59,0:13:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 丸太呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己去找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.80,0:13:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.14,0:13:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對外面說這裡的事也是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.85,0:13:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個我就當做勞務費收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.31,0:13:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是 我的CP!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.56,0:13:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.48,0:14:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.33,0:14:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這啥呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 放開我 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是收監體檢 別亂動哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.41,0:14:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五十嵐丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.08,0:14:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.92,0:15:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 都怪你在正式對決前偷打
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.39,0:15:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.26,0:15:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 臉好紅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少管我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是發燒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.48,0:15:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是麻醉還沒過去而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.24,0:15:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 你丫給我換衣服去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.36,0:15:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊? 醫生穿白衣有什麼不對的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.08,0:15:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有點抗性好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 白衣服很不妙好不好 各種的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.25,0:15:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸骨和肋骨有兩根 徹底斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然「利落」地斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.47,0:16:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣子 明天做不了「實驗」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我托創辦人取消或者換個時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.87,0:16:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骨頭折了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不會折
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.71,0:16:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千地清正的幹架
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.83,0:16:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別插手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.59,0:16:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指派律師?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我還有那個身份呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.13,0:16:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老本行是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.09,0:16:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個「死囚樂園」的創辦人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 想把能力者都聚集到此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是需要各種花招的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那什麼也是常有的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫁禍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.78,0:16:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說 那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.86,0:16:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我這兒有個特別擅長幹那個的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.95,0:16:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就搞了這麼一齣呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.08,0:17:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須得萬無一失才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.63,0:17:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是什麼大問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.55,0:17:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫的 鬼話連篇 死四眼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.88,0:17:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快解開 草泥馬快把這解開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這屎蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草泥馬 我絕對不會原諒你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須宰了你!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.60,0:17:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以哦 太得寸進尺的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒學過敬語麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}註釋：敬語是日語中表示尊敬的一種語言表達形式
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.95,0:17:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要學會「您」 「請」 「勞駕」之類的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.95,0:17:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}註釋：此處的敬語因為並無實際意義 因此翻成了漢語中常見的敬語
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「您」 「請」 「勞駕」!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉木創辦人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.67,0:17:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,負荷太大 會影響明天的「實驗」的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.46,0:17:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.72,0:18:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你在意了嗎 「實驗」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天你可要登台呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.73,0:18:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代號 「啄木鳥」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.65,0:18:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是你 五十嵐丸太 以及
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「烏鴉」 千地清正
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「罪之枝」的發病者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.00,0:18:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.81,0:18:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是能力者之間的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.92,0:18:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.59,0:18:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「實驗」在G棟可是日常行為
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.89,0:18:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏了的話能取得和之前的Dog Race
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.97,0:18:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法比擬的CastPoint
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.64,0:18:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和「Candy」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.48,0:18:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼能對你唯命是從
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.56,0:18:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.23,0:18:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外 要是你能一直取勝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.19,0:18:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定還能與你思念之人重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.65,0:19:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思念之人?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.78,0:19:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 長野事件中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.83,0:19:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全班都慘遭殺害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.62,0:19:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 準確來說並不是全班
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的 五十嵐丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.42,0:19:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是唯一被留下活口的人這一事實
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.59,0:19:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只瘋狂的怪物 似乎很欣賞你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.22,0:19:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 就是你說的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.81,0:19:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅衣男
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「罪之枝」能力的感染源
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.15,0:19:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是死囚樂園中最惡劣的居民
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.69,0:19:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(643,647)}Wretched Egg
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.69,0:19:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原罪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 是在這裡麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個紅衣男
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.20,0:19:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我見他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.66,0:19:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對要把他和你都宰掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.09,0:19:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就先登上明天的「實驗」——
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.05,0:19:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(557,642)}Carnival Corpse
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.05,0:19:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死肉祭的舞台吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.13,0:20:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(631,644)}Carnival Corpus
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.13,0:20:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死肉祭 ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.09,0:20:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會好玩到爆的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.73,0:20:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備完成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.82,0:20:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死肉祭——Carnival Corpus
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.65,0:20:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是「死囚樂園」最盛大的表演
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Deadman」——
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.03,0:20:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10年前的「Red Hole」發生之後
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所出現的「罪之枝」感染者們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.62,0:20:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了讓他們的病症
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.88,0:20:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是能將那特殊能力充分發揮而設的實驗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.38,0:20:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主要內容是 「Deadman」之間的互相殘殺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空前絕後 舉世無雙的娛樂活動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.85,0:20:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將要就此展開
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.34,0:21:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懂了麼 新人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.55,0:21:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我們再來一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.18,0:21:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要! 不要啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.26,0:22:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個月的「達人」到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.09,0:22:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放那兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.02,0:22:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個小鬼 是僥倖還是確有實力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.74,0:22:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我期待著呢 「啄木鳥」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.42,0:24:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只憑借對平凡日常的不捨之情
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.17,0:24:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是無法在那裡存活下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.56,0:24:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在名為扭曲的牢籠中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.52,0:24:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以詛咒之力互相殘殺取悅眾人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.39,0:24:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(573,700)}那就是「Deadman」之間的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.56,0:24:25.19,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(490,40)}#05 『死肉祭』
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.56,0:24:25.19,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs20\pos(640,20)}Carnival Corpse
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
