Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.39,0:22:54.77,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}淚止不住 一直流
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.97,0:23:03.36,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}恨 恨這不公的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.44,0:23:11.74,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}這座迷宮 想逃 卻沒有出口
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.07,0:23:15.87,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}追求自由的我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.96,0:23:25.17,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}倒立著 俯看天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.63,0:23:32.89,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我已經不是昨天的我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.26,0:23:39.98,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Shiny Shiny 夜空灑遍了星輝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.10,0:23:48.36,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}世界竟如此美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.65,0:23:55.33,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Shiny Shiny 月光載滿了希望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.37,0:24:03.21,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}世界是這般精彩
